</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="c">// Hash returns the hash to be signed by the sender.</span>
<span class="c">// It does not uniquely identify the transaction.</span>
<span class="k">func</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">fs</span> <span class="n">FrontierSigner</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">Hash</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tx</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Transaction</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">common</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Hash</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">rlpHash</span><span class="p">([]</span><span class="k">interface</span><span class="p">{}{</span>
        <span class="n">tx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">AccountNonce</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="n">tx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Price</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="n">tx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GasLimit</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="n">tx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Recipient</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="n">tx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Amount</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="n">tx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Payload</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="p">})</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>这里是 rlpHash，即先做 RLP 转换，然后做 Keccak256 hash。这里 hash 的数据，包括：账户 nonce，gas price，gas limint，目标地址，金额，额外数据。</p>

<div class="language-go highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
